,'Forbidden'=>'禁止访问','Forbidden: Rate limit exceeded. Please try later after %s seconds.'=>'禁止访问，因为请求过于频繁。请在 %s 秒后重试。','Form'=>'表单','Form Demo'=>'表单演示','Free and Helpful Courses'=>'免费且实用的课程','Free Forever after the third year.'=>'三年后永久免费。','Free Online Courses'=>'免费的在线课程','Free Online Documents'=>'免费的在线文档','From the PHP configuration file (such as enable-php-83.conf), confirm and modify this path:'=>'从 PHP 配置文件（如 enable-php-83.conf）中确认和修改这个路径：','Frontend Editor'=>'前端编辑器','Frontend tip shown before conversation messages. HTML is allowed.'=>'对话消息前显示的提示信息。允许使用HTML格式。','G3 License Code'=>'G3 授权码','G3-Web'=>'G3-Web','G3-Web helps you develop stronger wordpress theme. Dependencies: PHP 8.3+, WordPress 6.5+, Redis, fileinfo, %postname% permalink structure.'=>'G3-Web 帮助您开发更强大的 WordPress 主题。依赖：PHP 8.3+, WordPress 6.5+, Redis 扩展, fileinfo 扩展, %postname% 链接结构。','G3-Web helps you easily create a clean, modern and full-fledged website.'=>'G3-Web 帮助您更加便捷地构建安全、现代、功能齐全的网站。','G3-Web requires PHP 8.3+. Please upgrade your PHP version.'=>'G3-Web 需要 PHP 版本大于等于 8.3。请升级您的 PHP 版本。','G3-Web requires Redis server. Please make sure Redis is installed and running.'=>'G3-Web 依赖 Redis 服务。请确保您已经安装并启用了 Redis 扩展和服务。','G3-Web requires WordPress 6.5+. Please upgrade your WordPress version.'=>'G3-Web 需要 WordPress 版本大于等于 6.5。请升级您的 WordPress 版本。','G3-Web will create 2 databases in Redis to cache regular data and queue tasks. Regular data is stored in database 0, and queue tasks are stored in database 1.'=>'G3-Web 会在 Redis 中建立2个数据库，分别用来缓存常规数据和队列任务。常规数据存储在数据库 0 中，队列任务存储在数据库 1 中。','General Menu'=>'常规菜单','General Product'=>'常规商品','General Settings'=>'常规设置','Generate Invitation Code'=>'生成邀请码','Generate LLM Cache'=>'生成 LLM 缓存','Generate object-cache.php'=>'生成 object-cache.php 文件','Generate Sitemap'=>'生成站点地图','Generate the drop-in file <code><i>object-cache.php</i></code> in <code><i>wp-content</i></code> directory if it does not exist.'=>'当对象缓存的强化扩展文件不存在时，在 <code><i>wp-content</i></code> 目录生成新文件 <code><i>object-cache.php</i></code>。','Generated'=>'创建成功','Global Spec'=>'全局规格','Guest'=>'访客','Guest Name'=>'访客名称','Header Code'=>'页头区代码','Heartbeat'=>'心跳','Heartbeat interval in seconds. It is only used to keep the SSE connection alive. Default: 45, range: 30-60.'=>'心跳间隔（以秒为单位）。该参数仅用于保持SSE连接活跃。默认值：45，范围：30-60。','Help Link'=>'顶部帮助链接','Homepage Sidebar'=>'首页侧边栏','How many days ago you want to delete?'=>'您想要删除多少天以前的数据？','How to estimate the actual number of PHP files in your WordPress project?'=>'如何估算您的 WordPress 项目中实际 PHP 文件数量？','HTML Demo'=>'HTML演示','HTML element demo in admin panel.'=>'管理后台页面中的HTML元素演示。','https://www.jealer.com/'=>'https://www.jealer.com/','https://www.jealer.com/g3-system/'=>'https://www.jealer.com/g3-system/','ICP Code'=>'ICP备案号','If the title is empty, the title of the post will be used.'=>'如果标题为空，则直接使用当前内容的标题。','If you are conducting online business in mainland China, please be sure to input the ICP filing number issued by the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology of the People\'s Republic of China.'=>'如果您在中国大陆开展网络业务，请务必输入中华人民共和国工信部颁发的ICP备案号。','If you want to hide the developer mode menu, define the constant in your theme <code>define("G3_HIDE_DEVELOPER_MODE", true);</code>'=>'如果您想隐藏开发者模式的菜单，请在您的主题中定义常量 <code>define("G3_HIDE_DEVELOPER_MODE", true);</code>','Illegal request'=>'非法请求','Image upload & preview'=>'图片上传和预览','In G3-Web, all business data must be cached and queried through Redis.'=>'在 G3-Web 中，所有的业务数据都必需经过 Redis 缓存和查询。','In PHP templates, build a complete header to meet SEO requirements. In the page, only output the absolute necessary content.'=>'在 php 模板中，构建完整 header 以满足 SEO 要求。在页面当中，仅输出绝对必要的内容。','In template pages, most data is handled and interacted with by front-end JavaScript using rest-api and client-side caching (such as localStorage, indexDB). Reduce server pressure, reduce traffic transmission, improve page loading speed and user experience.'=>'在模板页面中，绝大部分数据都交由前端 JavaScript 利用 rest-api 和 客户端缓存（如 localStorage, indexDB）来处理和交互。减少服务