eMap Generator'=>'站点地图生成器','SKU System'=>'库存管理系统','Slug Param only allows English letters, numbers, and underscores'=>'别名参数仅允许英文字母、数字和下划线','Slug: Only supports English Letter'=>'别名：仅支持英文字母','SMS'=>'短信','SMTP Encryption'=>'SMTP加密方式','Social Accounts'=>'社交账号','Social Login'=>'社交登录','Sold'=>'已售','Sort'=>'排序','Spec option not found.'=>'规格选项不存在。','Specifications'=>'规格','Sponsor'=>'赞助','Start and end credits must be positive integers.'=>'起始和结束积分必需为正整数。','Start Credits'=>'起始积分','Starting from version 5.5 of WordPress, the functionality of multi-level and multi-page XML sitemaps has been loaded as a default core feature.'=>'从WP5.5版本开始，多层级多页面的XML站点地图功能已经作为核心功能默认载入。','Status'=>'状态','Stock'=>'库存','Store Management System'=>'门店管理系统','Store Messages'=>'消息存储','Submitted'=>'提交成功','Subscribe Login'=>'订阅登录','Subscribe Message'=>'订阅消息','Subscription Account'=>'订阅号','Swiper'=>'轮播图','Switch'=>'开关','Switched'=>'切换成功','System'=>'系统','System Admin'=>'系统管理员','System Camera'=>'系统相机','System Email'=>'系统邮件','System Generated'=>'系统生成','Template file does not exist: %s'=>'模板文件不存在：%s','Test Email Address'=>'测试邮箱地址','Textarea'=>'文本域','the <code>value</code> is an array.'=>'<code>value</code> 的值是个数组。','The actions below will flush the Rewrite / Options / Cache data, please make sure you have a backup before performing the action.'=>'下面的系列操作将强制刷新 重写规则、配置选项、缓存数据，操作前请先备份对应数据。','The announcement prompt that is fixedly displayed in front of the chat window. HTML is allowed.'=>'在聊天窗口前固定显示的公告提示。允许使用HTML格式。','The cache files will be stored in the /www/cache/nginx directory, and the cache files will be distributed across two levels of subdirectories. The shared memory area is named WORDPRESS and has a size of 100MB. If a cache file is not accessed within 60 minutes, Nginx will automatically clean it up.'=>'缓存文件将存放在 /www/cache/nginx 目录下, 缓存文件会分散到两级子目录中, 共享内存区 名为 WORDPRESS 大小为 100MB, 如果某个缓存文件在 60 分钟内未被访问, Nginx 会自动将其清理。','The current feature will be integrated after the requirement vote is approved.'=>'当前功能将在需求投票通过后集成。','The default message replied to users when the search is disabled and no message is found.'=>'当搜索功能被禁用且未匹配到任何回复时，将以此条默认消息回复用户。','The entire website will be immersed in a mournful mode with only black, white, and gray colors.'=>'全站将沉浸在只有黑白灰颜色的默哀模式中。','The expiration of the invitation code.'=>'邀请码的过期时间。','The field cannot be empty'=>'该选项不能为空','The following configuration recommendations are based on servers with 8G memory:'=>'下面的配置建议，是以 8G 内存配置的服务器为参考：','The Key that will call the latest posts. Default: n'=>'最新文章的事件Key。默认：n。','The links feature helps you manage your friendship links.'=>'链接功能帮助您管理友情链接。','The maximum length of the search keyword. Default: 16.'=>'搜索关键词的最大长度。默认 16。','The maximum number of news items returned in the Key-Event message. Default: 5.'=>'以图文格式显示的事件消息最大数量。默认：5。','The membership <a href="%s">duration</a> or <a href="%s">group</a> is not configured.'=>'<a href="%s">会员时长</a> 或 <a href="%s">自定义会员</a> 未配置。','The message sent to users when they Subscribe the WeChat Official Account.'=>'用户在订阅微信公众号时所接收到的系统消息。','The messages sent to the WeChat Official Account will be stored in the database.'=>'用户在微信公众号里发送的信息，将被存储进数据库。','The nginx server receives the user request'=>'Nginx 服务器接收用户请求','The No Theme Mode, will greatly improve your application performance and server load capacity.'=>'无主题模式，将大幅提高您的应用性能和服务器负载能力。','The number of items displayed per page in the form list of admin panel.'=>'管理面板中表单列表的每页显示条数','The number of posts to be generated for each post type.<br>Default: <code>2000</code>.'=>'每个内容类型所生成的内容数量。<br>默认：<code>2000</code>。','The payment method used to pay for the invitation code.'=>'用来购买邀请码的支付方式。','The price of the invitation code.'=>'邀请码的价格。','The purpose of OPCache is to improve the efficiency of PHP code through precompiling PHP code. Therefore, our core goal is to reduce the number of file reads and compilation overhead, find a balance between memory usage, cache hit, and code update mechanism.'=>'OPCache的作用是通过预编译PHP代码，从而提高PHP代码的执行效率。所以，我们配置OPCache的核心目标是减少文件读取次数和编译的开销，在内存使用、缓存命中、代码更新机制之间找到平衡。','The role name has been initialized.'=>'角色名称已被初始化。','The role slug can only contain English and numbers.'=>'角色别名仅支持英文字母和数字。','The start credits must be less than the end credits.'=>'起始积分必需小于结束积分。','The system will replace <code>"wp-login.php"</code> with the new address <code>"/oa/$url"</code> below.'=>'系统将使用下方配置的新地址 <code>"/oa/$url"</code> 来替代 <code>"wp-login.php"</code>。','The system will replace the default email templates of the site with custom email templates.'=>'系统将使用自定义邮件模板来替代默认模板。','The system will use SMTP to send emails.'=>'系统将使用 SMTP 来发送邮件。','The template "%s" is not implemented yet. Please complete your own theme.'=>'模板 "%s" 尚未实现。请完成您的主题设计和开发。','The theme mode is automatically determined based on the cookie <code>jui-theme</code>. The frontend template HTML element will have classes such as <code>dark</code>, <code>j-theme-indigo</code>, etc.'=>'根据 cookie <code>jui-theme</code> 主题数据，自动为前端模板 HTML 添加 class，如 <code>dark</code>, <code>j-theme-indigo</code> 等。','The theme you configure on the Appearance-Theme page is the main theme of the system. When the option corresponding to the multi-theme mode is empty, the main theme will be used first by default.'=>'您在 外观-主题 页面中配置的主题是系统的主主题。当对应多主题模式的选项为空时，默认优先使用主主题。','The URL you visited is illegal.'=>'您正在访问不合法的网络地址。','Theme Assembly'=>'主题装配','Theme Customize'=>'主题自定义','Theme Description'=>'主题描述','Theme Editor'=>'主题编辑器','Theme for low-end browsers'=>'低端浏览器主题','Theme for mobile'=>'手机端主题','Theme Mode'=>'主题模式','Theme Name'=>'主题名称','Theme URL'=>'主题项目网址','This tab is for Caddy security configuration advice.'=>'当前选项卡是关于Caddy服务器安全配置建议。','This tab is for hybrid theme development advice.'=>'当前标签页是关于混动主题开发建议。','This tab is for Nginx FastCGI Cache configuration advice.'=>'当前标签页是关于 Nginx FastCGI 缓存配置建议。','This tab is for Nginx security configuration advice.'=>'当前选项卡是关于Nginx服务器安全配置建议。','This tab is for PHP OPCache configuration advice.'=>'当前标签页是关于 PHP OPCache 缓存配置建议。