 your account and security.'=>'您即将离开本站，请注意您的账号和财产安全。','You can add custom SEO data for each page.'=>'您可以为每一个页面自定义SEO数据。','You can add widgets to archive sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到归档页侧边栏。','You can add widgets to homepage sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到首页侧边栏。','You can add widgets to page sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到页面侧边栏。','You can add widgets to post sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到文章页侧边栏。','You can add widgets to product sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到商品页侧边栏。','You can add widgets to search sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到搜索页侧边栏。','You can add widgets to shop sidebar.'=>'您可以添加小工具到商城页侧边栏。','You can choose a theme for low-end browsers that do not support ES2015 standard.'=>'您可以为不支持ES2015标准的低端浏览器选择一个主题。','You can choose to use G3-Sitemap instead of the default WordPress sitemap in the security settings, as the default sitemap may expose sensitive user information.'=>'您可以在安全设置中选择使用G3-Sitemap取代WordPress默认的sitemap，因为默认的sitemap会暴露用户敏感信息。','You can configure different theme templates for different types of devices to improve user experience.'=>'您可以为不同类型的设备配置不同的主题模板，以提升用户体验。','You can customize the contact form template by overriding the template file <code>/templates/form/index.php</code>.'=>'您可以通过覆盖模板文件 <code>/templates/form/index.php</code> 来自定义联系表单的模板。','You can manually add the above script to the head tag of the theme template to replace the automatic theme assembly function set above.'=>'您可以手动在主题模板的 head 标签中添加以上脚本，取代上方设置的自动主题装配功能。','You can provide the RSS feed address to partners or users for subscribing to receive content from your platform.'=>'您可以把RSS地址提供给合作伙伴或用户，用来订阅获取您平台内容。','You can Select a theme for mobile devices.'=>'您可以为手机设备选择一个主题。','You can visit the current address to generate local cache files of the sitemap.'=>'您可以访问当前地址，生成 sitemap 本地缓存文件。','You need to define the cache file storage directory, such as: '=>'您需定义缓存文件存储目录，如：','Your G3 Web has been activated.'=>'您的G3-Web已经激活。','Your G3-Web expires in %s'=>'您的 G3-Web 过期时间：%s','Your message has been sent successfully. We will get back to you shortly.'=>'您的消息已经发送成功。我们会尽快与您联系。']];
